stories.title: Guwahati's international future in doubt
stories.subTitle: India v England, 5th ODI, Guwahati
stories.summary: The future of Guwahati as an international venue is in doubt following the serious crowd disturbances which followed the abandonment of Sunday's ODI between India and England

stories.title: Strauss sympathetic to fans' anger
stories.subTitle: India v England, 5th ODI, Guwahati
stories.summary: Following the riots and anger from supporters at Guwahat, the England batsman Andrew Strauss has sympathised with the fans' frustration after the match was called off

stories.title: Fans run riot after abandonment
stories.subTitle: India v England, 5th ODI, Guwahati
stories.summary: Guwahati's standing as an international venue is under serious threat in the aftermath of the fifth India-England ODI where crowd trouble erupted when the umpires called off play because of a wet outfield

stories.title: India v England, 5th ODI, Guwahati
stories.subTitle: April 9, 2006
stories.summary: Match home for the fifth ODI between India and England at Guwahati on April 9, 2006

stories.title: No play on a damp day
stories.subTitle: India v England, 5th ODI, Guwahati
stories.summary: Damp conditions at Guwahati meant that the only game of the series that was scheduled on a Sunday had to be called off even a single ball being bowled
